Class PQTreeList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - object type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<PQTree<T>>, java.util.Collection<PQTree<T>>, java.util.List<PQTree<T>>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class PQTreeList<T>
extends java.util.ArrayList<PQTree<T>>
    This class implements list of PQ-Trees that support all list operations and several others. All these special operations lighten work with rules that applies to several trees. Rules are applied separately for each tree and they are merged together if needed.
